<h2 align="center">Research Associate Opportunity</h2>
<div class="container-fluid mt-5" style="max-width: 800px;">
    <h4>Position: Research Associate</h4>
    <p>We are seeking a few motivated Research Associates (RAs) to join the Distributed Systems Research group at the
        <a href="{{ site.url }}">Centre for Networked Intelligence (CNI)</a>. The RAs will be actively involved in one of the following research
